## Examples

<span data-ttu-id="c3983-223">次の例では、現在のスキームを取得します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c3983-223">The following example gets the current Scheme.</span></span>

```csharp
BasicHttpBinding binding = new BasicHttpBinding();
string thisScheme = binding.Scheme;
```

  
  
## Examples

<span data-ttu-id="c3983-240">次の例では、ReceiveSynchronously 値を取得します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c3983-240">This example gets the ReceiveSynchronously value.</span></span>

```csharp
BasicHttpBinding binding = new BasicHttpBinding();
IBindingRuntimePreferences s = (binding as IBindingRuntimePreferences);
bool receiveSynchronously = s.ReceiveSynchronously;
```
